pageContext.claim: “ICE. They take out thousands and thousands of MS-13 killers a year and bring them the hell back out of our country.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is inflating the numbers quite a bit. Immigration and Customs Enforcement deported more than 2,000 members of MS-13 during his first years in office, and pushed over the 2,000 mark largely because of enforcement surges conducted in 2018 and 2019.
